data.title: Vaduz - centre of culture
data.meta_description: Sport, relaxation, culture - visiting Liechtenstein is a stimulating experience at any time of the year. Take time to discover our small country and you will see that there really is something for everyone, from solo travellers to families.
data.text:
Attractions in Vaduz

Vaduz is the capital of Liechtenstein and offers a variety of attraction and events.

Museum mile Vaduz

Experience 6 museums door to door in the St√§dtle Vaduz and enjoy varied exhibitions and special presentations.

Sculptures in Vaduz

Attentive visitors will notice a large number of sculptures by world-famous artists as they walk around Vaduz.

Princely cinema

Experience a princely movie experience in the Old Cinema Vaduz. Old cinema charm meets state-of-the-art cinema LED technology and offers wonderful insights behind the scenes of Vaduz Castle.

Guided tours through Vaduz

Discover the capital of Liechtenstein on one of the guided tours through Vaduz.
